resources.string: Ikhodi yesevisi engalungile efakiwe. Sicela uzame futhi.
Ikhodi engalungile yesevisi ifakwe kaningi. Ukuvala idivayisi.
Lokhu kuzosetha kabusha idivayisi yakho. Yonke idatha yomsebenzisi izosulwa kusuka kudivayisi.

Idivayisi yakho ihlangabezane nenkinga ngenkathi izama ukuxhumeka kunethiwekhi edinga ukusethwa kabusha. Ungathanda ukusetha kabusha idivayisi? Lokhu kuzosusa i-akhawunti yakho kusukela kule divayisi kodwa ngeke kususe idatha yakho yomuntu siqu.
Inethiwekhi ilungiselela amasevisi wakho. Sicela ulinde…
Ukubuyekeza iphrofayela akukwazanga ukuqedwa. Sicela uzame futhi emuva kwesikhathi. Uma inkinga iqhubeka, kuzomele uxhumane Isevisi Yamakhasimende.
"Ilungiselela idivayisi yakho izwi nedatha. Sicela ulinde…"
Idivayisi yenziwe yasebenza. Cindezela ku-OK ukuze uqhubeke.
I-PRL ibuyekeziwe. CIndezela ku-OK ukuze uqhubeke.
Ukwenza idivayisi isebenze kuhlulekile. Uma inkinga iqhubeka, kungenzeka udinge ukuxhumana ne-Isevisi Yamakhasimende.

"Isexwayiso: I-SCRTN izoqalisa ukusebenza okulandelayo iphinde iqalise kabusha ifoni, ingabe uqinisekile ngokuqhubeka? Setha kabusha i-MDN ibuyele kokuzenzakalelayo kwasekuqaleni Setha kabusha i-MSID iye kokuzenzakalelayo kwasekuqaleni Setha kabusha Isilothi esingu-1 NAI kube ngokuzenzakalelayo kwasekuqaleni Setha kabusha iphasiwedi yesilothi esingu-1 NAI sibe ngokuzenzakalelayo kwasekuqaleni"
Ngesikhathi sokulungiselela, isevisi yakho yeselula kungenzeka ingatholakali okwesikhashana. Lokhu kuzomele kuthathe amaminithi ambalwa kuphela.
